{"tid":1282954,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 密碼錯十次資料刪光光","createTime":"2019-07-03T16:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T16:35:53.000Z","uid":92170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8b90feacbedca6996a3220a51be6a0aa346aab1c","tid":1282954,"uid":92170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">iPhone 密碼錯十次資料刪光光</span></span><br />\n<br />\n在 iPhone X 或之後的型號上，前往「設定」&gt;「Face ID 與密碼」。在其他較早期的 iPhone 型號上，前往「設定」&gt;「Touch ID 與密碼」。在沒有 Touch ID 的裝置上，前往「設定」&gt;「密碼」。<br />\n<br />\n清除資料：選擇是否在輸入 10 次錯誤密碼後自動清除裝置。如果不啟用此選項，在輸入 10 次錯誤密碼後，你會需要在 iTunes 中還原裝置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT204060&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=2295792b\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT204060</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IOS快速連按5次電源鍵，即時停用Face ID / 指紋登入</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我無野講!! 6549 9452民陣<br />\n<br />\n認人程序疑犯戴浴帽口罩　盧偉聰：要尊重合理權利<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/認人程序疑犯戴浴帽口罩-盧偉聰-要尊重合理權利\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E6%88%B4%E6%B5%B4%E5%B8%BD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=38eca7ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E8%AA%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E6%88%B4%E6%B5%B4%E5%B8%BD%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-%E8%A6%81%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E5%90%88%E7%90%86%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9&h=bfdd3cb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/認人程序疑犯戴浴帽口罩-盧偉聰-要尊重合理權利</a>"},{"pid":"9d6